bio.info: Permic is a dragon that was previously a lizard because of an experiment. He's mostly rude and stubborn, but can be nice at times. He has dark red scales, grey fingerless gloves, and pink shoes.
bio.backstory: Permic used to be a lizard, rather than a dragon, for 13 years. Then, just after his 14th birthday, he wandered off to a lab that turns regular creatures into mythical ones. He was dosed with some suspicious medicine, but didn't feel anything, so he went to bed. The next morning, however, he felt different. He had horns on his head and he had gained the ability to breathe fire (He always had the pyrokinesis abilities since he was a lizard dw about that). He had been turned into a dragon. His first reaction was to find a way to get back into his older form, but he hasn't been able to do so. He has gotten used to this new form, however he does still look for ways to get back to his older form.

bio.info: A tamoan chihuahua who is usually very nice and active, but can be overconfident and cocky at times. He has yellow-orange fur, green shoes, and a blue collar. He is mostly clueless about the world around him, but he would really like to explore it more and make friends along the way.
bio.backstory: Sparky's from Planet Tamoa. He has been living in his hometown for 11 years. It has been very peaceful and happy in that hometown, until it was attacked and war broke out. The president of the town instructed the youth to evacuate the planet to a partner planet via an emergency space ship. Sparky's trip was going fine, until the space ship started going out of his control and went crazy, and ended up crashing on the planet called Yaretza. He was seriously injured from the crash but thanks to somebody healing him, he was able to recover. The events still come in his mind at times, but he stays calm and acts like it never happened most of the time.

bio.info: A man of three identities, with the ability of changing between them, on accident. Tho they're pretty subtle right now, they can strengthen in a way or another. 3'9 in height, a guy that likes to explore on his own, or not try and spend time with the group. And a utility belt where he keeps his shortsword around his waist. He may resemble Spectra in many ways, both being Tanukis, but Sky's tail is slightly larger, as well as being a bit fluffier.
bio.backstory: As a traveling warrior, he's seen many places and people. Through these travels, he has gained battle experience by simply mimicking what others do. Sometimes you can spot him with a leaf on his head. Being a Tanuki, he gets rather lonely, as there is almost no fellow Tanuki in the world. Spectra is the only exception to this, but as she came from a different planet, it's a bit awkward for him to approach her.

bio.info: A happy-go-lucky spirit that enjoys to be a part of groups, but usually never sticks around much. She's only been with one group within her spiritual time, but time has a funny way of saying fuck you.
bio.backstory: A different type of spirit that, unlike other spirits, actually chooses to stay in this plane of existence to supply blessings to people in their times of need. Her past before death is a mystery.

bio.info: Rainbow is a cautious hedgehog(?) who trusts pretty much nobody in fear of being captured, but otherwise will try his best to help people who need it. However, due to this fear he might act irrational at times, even going as far as harming people he's never even met. He's a purple hedgehog(?) with six spines/quills; three on each side of his head, an elongated wolf-like muzzle, white chest fur hidden by a tan velcro disc and standard blue shoes.

I'm not even mad anymore. I'm just disappointed.

Ira.name: Ira
repelquote: ..Why would you do this to yourself...?

bio.info: Ira is a shy and timid altarian who's shorter than most, if not all, of the group. When not shy, she's really kind and is willing to help out anyone she trusts. She has white fur, pink shoes, and a purple and pink scarf. It's believed that she has very unstable psychic power deep within her that she can't harness by normal means...
bio.backstory: Ira originally was from Altaria, where she had lived a peaceful(?) life. When war had broken out, she was the first to evacuate. She had no idea where to go, so she had just went to a random planet (which was conveniently(?) the same planet that the group was on).
bio.likes: People whom she can trust, comfortable spots, warmness.

bio.backstory: Neo Nimbasa of Universe 1 was born during the era of peace after a certain event high above was dealt with by the grandmasters. Due to his job with Tempest HQ, he has gained quite the fame with both his royal life and his good feats.
